item.title: 3-handle construction on II$_1$ factors
item.description: arXiv:2504.02003v1 Announce Type: new Abstract: We find a subtle modification to the construction of Chifan-Ioana-Kunnawalkam Elayavalli, which yields a drastic simplification of the proof of the existence of two non Gamma non elementarily equivalent II$_1$ factors.
item.dc:creator: David Gao, Srivatsav Kunnawalkam Elayavalli, Gregory Patchell
